{
  "stem": "14552.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they-- we, we got the word that this and this-- count the bricks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Such and such a number is not mortared.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It's not cemented in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So you push it out-- when you're there and it comes, push it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "When the gas comes, push that wall out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they-- meanwhile, they were telling the-- telegraphing because in Theresienstadt, there was the equipment because there was a model camp and they had equipment there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They telegraphed the Russians that if you don't show up by such and such time, so many people will be gassed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they did show up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they came, and we were not able-- they did not take us for destruction.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then they saw what, what was happening there, emaciated bodies.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And my skin was brown and my bones.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "There was no longer any flesh.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "The color of the skin was black.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And they handed the people beans-- bacon and beans in cans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And people ate it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And more than half of the camp died of dysentery.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I couldn't stand there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I couldn't go and grab for it so much, so I got very little.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I too got dysentery.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But mine-- I didn't eat enough of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And so again--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were together.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [SIGHS] we couldn't-- the camp couldn't be taken-- after we were freed, we could not be moved because everybody there had dysentery.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were no-- there was no doctor around to-- there was no medicine around.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Russians came-- they-- I don't think they expected this kind of a-- of a, human, human destruction.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And so they, they gave us all that food from their-- from their rations.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that killed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That killed.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
